{"tid":612725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國4月1日嚴管VPN     大批網民斷線崩潰","createTime":"2018-04-01T05:46:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:32:27.000Z","uid":39464,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2d0680f1fe3839a4feb5923aa8eb16253f08da3e","tid":612725,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:46:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phppFelDo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phppFelDo.jpg&h=ba53da41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中國於今天4月1日開始，對所有未經授權和核准的VPN展開封鎖，微博開始出現大量網民崩潰哀嚎，痛陳自己突然斷線無法上網。<br />\n<br />\n據《德國之聲》報導，中國工信部於去年1月發布通知，指出至今年3月31日為止會對無證經營、超出範圍經營的VPN展開追查，工信部發言人張峰強調，此舉主要是清理不合規範的VPN服務，不會影響守法的企業與個人。<br />\n<br />\n然而，中國微博今日哀鴻遍野，網民紛紛發現自己原本使用的VPN無法連上網路，有人只是掛著VPN想聽國外音樂也不行，一名網友更是因為無法上網搶購偶像限量商品而痛哭失聲。VPN災情連學術網路也不放過，一名學子透露他根本不能查文獻資料，也就完全無法寫論文了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2383258\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2383258&d=DkDoBY7nHE9Dk66rJNTU4TANphTrK3OAdhrcB0lChBw%3D&h=3264afc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2383258&h=11920918\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2383258</a>"},{"pid":"da5a1731d18d58fdc34e05306d9d7d421a79eaf2","tid":612725,"uid":9171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:48:16.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c1260e215a491ebde08bcf02c61b2e34985d87b","tid":612725,"uid":179962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:50:22.000Z","msg":"我部IPX都用唔到VPN"},{"pid":"461ec1a9366887e2ca2c36be591f038ec528f43e","tid":612725,"uid":24513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T05:50:51.000Z","msg":"Subst